n ataa karne waale mujhe rizq de aur mere ayaal ko rizq de apne fazl se kyu-keh yaqeenan Tu bade fazl ka maalik hai.", "Urdu": "اے بہترین ذات جس سے مانگا جاتا ہے! اور بہترین عطا کرنےوالے مجھے رزق دے اور میرے عیال کو رزق دے اپنے فضل سے کیوں کہ یقیناً تو بڑے فضل کا مالک ہے۔", "RArabic": "YAA KHAI-RAL MAS-OO-LEENA WA YAA KHAI-RAL MO’TEENA UR-ZUQNEE WAR-ZUQ E’YAA-LEE MIN FAZLE-KA FA-INNA-KA ZUL FAZLIL A’ZEEME.", "ArabicText1": "يَا خَيْرَ الْمَسْئُوْلِيْنَ وَيَا خَيْرَ الْمُعْطِيْنَ اُرْزُقْنِىْ وَارْزُقْ عِيَالِىْ مِنْ فَضْلِكَ فَاِنَّكَ ذُوالْفَضْلِ الْعَظِيْمِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSig